tps://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRWv_42QKFh8pa9LYycPAiCyxIYeV1gGZCkaw";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:1080;s:6:"height";i:1080;s:6:"source";s:49:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/450500768981803462/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:59:{i:0;s:129:"Get ready to move twist reach and play as Tatis leads this one hour active Chair Yoga class filmed LIVE at the Yoga Vista Studio.";i:1;s:25:"Tatis includes sequences.";i:2;s:126:"Chair Yoga Chair Yoga invites you to find mobility in a way that is soft and gentle but also really supportive and beneficial.";i:3;s:102:"This 17 min practice invites awareness and integrity into the body specifically the line of the spine.";i:4;s:103:"Activate the muscles that help you find length up through the spine for better posture and energy flow.";i:5;s:92:"Why Chair Yoga is Great An experienced yoga teacher doesnt fight students hesitancy to move.";i:6;s:235:"It makes much more sense to meet the student where heshe is energetically start with basic body and breath awareness then continue to small movement and then gradually expand the parameters of movement until the whole body is involved.";i:7;s:32:"What is a Chair Yoga class like.";i:8;s:132:"Chair Yoga classes with Stacie or from Sunlight Chair Yoga videos or books gives you the full benefits any other yoga class entails.";i:9;s:111:"Centering yoga warm-ups yoga exercises postures concentration breathing exercises guided relaxation meditation.";i:10;s:21:"Why teach Chair Yoga.";i:11;s:141:"These fun and unique sessions are designed for people of all ages and stages with or without health challenges as well as anyone new to yoga.";i:12;s:62:"Chair Yoga provides all the wonderful health benefits of yoga.";i:13;s:66:"It improves fitness flexibility balance strength and coordination.";i:14;s:30:"It relaxes your body and mind.";i:15;s:17:"It elevates your.";i:16;s:22:"Free chair yoga class.";i:17;s:24:"Posted by 3 minutes ago.";i:18;s:22:"Free chair yoga class.";i:19;s:79:"I made an online chair yoga course and the first class is available on YouTube.";i:20;s:34:"Hope someone here finds it useful.";i:21;s:100:"Chair Yoga is perfect for beginners looking to learn poses before transitioning to a mat yoga class.";i:22;s:175:"Baby Boomers and Beyond Beginners Big Bodied Students Students Recovering or Healing from Injuries Mobility Impaired Students seeking a challenging yet gentle yoga experience.";i:23;s:265:"Chair yoga classes perth Support your health wellbeing and posture through this gentle and accessible class Blending together a variety of movements and postures designed to develop strength and stability whilst improving awareness balance mobility and flexibility.";i:24;s:148:"Chair yoga is an ideal exercise for those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain carpal tunnel syndrome osteoporosis and multiple sclerosis.";i:25;s:122:"It may also benefit people over a certain age who have trouble moving through the up and down motions of traditional yoga.";i:26;s:42:"Chair yoga allows them to stay stabilized.";i:27;s:124:"Chair Yoga Classes online with Ki Gentle yoga postures in or near a chair to increase range of motion for injury prevention.";i:28;s:84:"Develop main muscle groups to improve overall health and maintain your independence.";i:29;s:75:"Practice simple breathing techniques for stress management and mindfulness.";i:30;s:166:"This gentle yoga class is designed with 8 sequences of great a variety of preparations and poses to introduce a novice student to what is possible in a yoga practice.";i:31;s:58:"Seated Poses in the chair and on the floor Reclined Poses.";i:32;s:155:"Chair yoga sequences can also be done while working in front of the computer to give the body a gentle massage and stretch if one is seated for long hours.";i:33;s:70:"So chair yoga sequences are also beneficial for people with desk jobs.";i:34;s:108:"Please click on the sequence title to view the complete chair yoga sequence with detailed overview and cues.";i:35;s:105:"This course will give you three full-length chair yoga practices as well as a breakdown of 30 yoga poses.";i:36;s:95:"Its a great course for anyone looking to teach yoga to seniors or people with reduced mobility.";i:37;s:82:"This is not a certification course and is simply meant to be educational for yoga.";i:38;s:188:"This class is lead in a Gentle Yoga style that makes yoga do-able for beginners or anyone who wants the deeper benefits of yoga without any requirements of balance strength or flexibility.";i:39;s:104:"The class is primarily seated movements but occasionally some supported standing movements are included.";i:40;s:41:"Students experience the benefits of yoga.";i:41;s:136:"Chair Yoga Level 1 20 Shoulder Rotations in a Chair Pt3 Dan Ward In this class explore how the shoulders rotate in the transverse plane.";i:42;s:143:"Chair Yoga Level 1 20 Standing Poses In a Chair Pt4 Dan Ward Traction the spine in puppy dog and then explore warrior 2 all with chair support.";i:43;s:48:"Chair Yoga Level 1 20 Strong Chair Pt5 Dan Ward.";i:44;s:28:"Chair Yoga Class Video 2500.";i:45;s:49:"This video includes a 60 minute chair yoga class.";i:46;s:32:"Chair Yoga Class Video quantity.";i:47;s:19:"What is Chair Yoga.";i:48;s:116:"Seniors or those who have mobility issues avoid unnecessary movements due to fear of falling or injuring themselves.";i:49;s:109:"With limited movements the limbs get stiff reducing the range of motion causing aches and pains in the limbs.";i:50;s:131:"Chair yoga is a type of gentle yoga that teaches participants how to achieve traditional yoga poses while safely seated in a chair.";i:51;s:93:"Students duplicate yoga poses traditionally done on hands and knees on the floor or on a mat.";i:52;s:72:"All positions are done while seated in a chair rather than on the floor.";i:53;s:103:"If you or someone you know would like to attend a class take a look at our Chair Yoga Classes on offer.";i:54;s:142:"If you are interested in finding out more about how yoga can help on a one-to-one basis take a look at our One-to-one Accessible Yoga service.";i:55;s:125:"If you are a care home interested in bringing yoga to your residents and staff take a look at our Yoga in Care Homes service.";i:56;s:65:"Gentle yoga classes are done seated or using a chair for balance.";i:57;s:100:"In addition you dont need to get down on the floor wear special clothes or have expensive equipment.";i:58;s:136:"This makes them perfect for people of all ages and fitness levels including seniors those with injuries long term health conditions and.";}}